# FitnessTracker Skill Entry

Canonical skill definition:
- `.agents/skills/fitnesstracker-ios-sim-flow/SKILL.md`

Current workflow contract:
- Use XCUITest as the single UI automation driver.
- Do not use legacy Appium/JS integration tests.
- Use `.agents/skills/fitnesstracker-ios-sim-flow/scripts/run_sim_flow.sh` for screenshot capture.

Legacy Appium parity coverage now maps to:
- `FitnessTrackerUITests/FitnessTrackerUITests/testAddWorkoutFlow`
- `FitnessTrackerUITests/CriticalPathUITests/testOnboardingFlowSkipToHome`
- `FitnessTrackerUITests/CriticalPathUITests/testTimerFlowStartsWhileLogging`
- `FitnessTrackerUITests/CriticalPathUITests/testHealthKitSettingsFlowReachable`
